d iot sectors founded in  the company held its hello world at the  international consumer electronics show in las vegas where zdnet cited the hypr solution as one of the shows top  innovations alongside those of billiondollar tech players in the legacy sphere now venturebacked by rtp ventures boldstart ventures and mesh ventures the company is under rapid expansion and recently announced that the server component of the hypr platform is officially fido® certified the company partners with leading enterprises introducing secure voice face touch eye palm and behavioral recognition to consumerfacing and internal employee applications iot system makers represent a growing portion of the companys portfolio  im thrilled to see gartner identify hypr as a cool vendor as the internet of things takes shape around us industry leaders are looking for powerful ways to decentralize and secure digital identity the hypr vision for a secure connected world built upon decentralized authentication is one that enterprises are following with great interest said nicholas donofrio ibm fellow emeritus ibm executive vice president innovation and technology ret and founder nmd consulting llc with household names in the banking sector already deploying hypr to millions of users its for us great to see gartner designate the company as a cool vendor said ann johnson vice president of the enterprise cybersecurity group at microsoft what they are doing for the authentication space really is cool the rising number of connected devices and increasing amount of data breaches highlights the importance of biometric authentication especially within the financial space said george avetisov ceo and cofounder of hypr we believe the cool vendor designation affirms hyprs commitment to ensure biometric data remains safely offline and stored on users local devices by leveraging decentralized authentication we have a crack team of the best and brightest who are reinventing identity and access management our approach is disruptive and innovative yet to us customer feedback and this gartner designation validate that our solution is mature enough for user populations into the many millions the report is available to gartner clients for download at cool vendors in transforming multichannel to unified retail commerce  gartner disclaimer gartner does not endorse any vendor product or service depicted in our research publications and does not advise technology users to select only those vendors with the highest ratings or other designation gartner research publications consist of the opinions of gartners research organization and should not be construed as statements of fact gartner disclaims all warranties expressed or implied with respect to this research including any warranties of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose about hypr  hypr is the first authentication solution to unite frictionless digital experiences with bestinclass security and  percent privacy protection hypr provide enterprises an endtoend solution for deploying decentralized biometric authentication securely across millions of users hypr software is integrated into employee and customerfacing applications to eliminate fraud enhance user experience and increase revenue additional information is available at httpswwwhyprcom  media contact north th agency inc  gveleznacom to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesbiometricauthenticationproviderhyprcorpnamedbygartneracoolvendortransformingmultichanneltounifiedretailcommercehtml source hypr corp the information on this page is provided by pr newswire all rights reserved reproduction or redistribution of this content without prior written consent from pr newswire is strictly prohibited is not responsible for this content learn more about this service about pr newswire the information on this page is provided by pr newswire the business journals is not responsible for this content learn more